<title type="html"><![CDATA[Average size for music engine]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5571&amp;p=50685#p50685"><![CDATA[
As for driver sizes (code + LUTs, not including music data), most of the ones I've written (SN76489, YM2413, YM2151, YM2612, AY-3-8910, Konami SCC, SID) are between 1.5 and 3.5 kB in size. That's just ROM, though - some of them can use over 1 kB of RAM depending on how many channels you're using.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1181">mic_</a> — Thu Sep 17, 2009 12:19 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
